Detailed Description

Parameter Block Class Interface.

Author:
Carlos Eduardo Mello
Date:
3/5/2009
This class consists of floating point vector which is used by MuM to hold and access extra parameters in a note.These parameters are optional, and usually only used by notes with special argument needs, for Csound output.
